OL,3,CSeveral GCSE and A-level exams could
OL,4,Cbe taken on screen from 2030
OL,6,FSeveral exams across GCSEs and A-
OL,7,Flevels could be taken on screens from
OL,8,Fthe end of the decade under new
OL,9,Fproposals from the exams watchdog.
OL,11,FProposals in a consultation launched
OL,12,Fby regulator Ofqual on Thursday could
OL,13,Fsee some GCSE exams in smaller-entry
OL,14,Fsubjects, including some languages and
OL,15,Fin any A-level exams except maths,
OL,16,Fmove onto screens from around 2030.
