OL,3,CSeveral GCSE and A-level exams could
OL,4,Cbe taken on screen from 2030
OL,6,FOfqual is asking for views on allowing
OL,7,Feach of the four exam boards to put
OL,8,Fforward two new specifications, each
OL,9,Fto involve assessment on screen rather
OL,10,Fthan the traditional pen and paper.
OL,12,FIf all of these were approved, it
OL,13,Fwould mean a total of eight new GCSE,
OL,14,FAS or A-level exams with at least some
OL,15,Fcomponent assessed digitally.
