OL,3,CSeveral GCSE and A-level exams could
OL,4,Cbe taken on screen from 2030
OL,6,FThe regulator is also proposing that
OL,7,Fdevices to take exams on screen would
OL,8,Fneed to be provided, rather than
OL,9,Fallowing students to use their own
OL,10,Fpersonal phones, laptops or tablets.
OL,12,FLetting pupils use their own devices
OL,13,Fwould be unfair, Sir Ian said.
OL,15,F"You'd have some that had state-of-the-
OL,16,Fart, fancy Apple Macs, and you'd have
OL,17,Fsome that would have very slow,
OL,18,Fpotentially vulnerable devices," he
OL,19,Fadded.
