OL,3,CSeveral GCSE and A-level exams could
OL,4,Cbe taken on screen from 2030
OL,6,FPepe Di'Iasio, general secretary of
OL,7,Fthe Association of School and College
OL,8,FLeaders, said: "We're really pleased
OL,9,Fthat Ofqual is exploring the potential
OL,10,Ffor on-screen assessment in the
OL,11,Ffuture, as there are several possible
OL,12,Fbenefits to utilising digital
OL,13,Ftechnology for exams.
OL,15,F"This would represent a significant
OL,16,Fchange, with many practical issues,
OL,17,Fand a measured approach is the right
OL,18,Fway to proceed."
