OL,3,CSeveral GCSE and A-level exams could
OL,4,Cbe taken on screen from 2030
OL,6,FThe subjects that would not be
OL,7,Feligible for on-screen exams at this
OL,8,Fpoint include A-level and GCSE maths,
OL,9,Fas well as GCSE English language,
OL,10,Fliterature, combined science, biology,
OL,11,Fchemistry, physics, history,
OL,12,Fgeography, religious studies, French,
OL,13,FSpanish and business.
OL,15,FGCSE German had just over 32,000
OL,16,Fentries in provisional Ofqual figures
OL,17,Ffor 2025, and therefore would be
OL,18,Feligible.
