OL,3,CSeveral GCSE and A-level exams could
OL,4,Cbe taken on screen from 2030
OL,6,FEducation Secretary Bridget Phillipson
OL,7,Fsaid: "Technology is at the forefront
OL,8,Fof this Government's mission to spread
OL,9,Fopportunity and modernise our
OL,10,Feducation system.
OL,12,F"We know interest in on-screen exams
OL,13,Fis growing, and aligning assessment
OL,14,Fwith an increasingly digital world
OL,15,Fcould bring valuable benefits,
OL,16,Fincluding for children with Send.
