OL,3,CSeveral GCSE and A-level exams could
OL,4,Cbe taken on screen from 2030
OL,6,F"But it's also important any shift is
OL,7,Fphased, controlled and above all,
OL,8,Ffair. We will continue to work closely
OL,9,Fwith Ofqual and the wider sector to
OL,10,Fmake sure we protect the high
OL,11,Fstandards and integrity of our exam
OL,12,Fsystem and retain the confidence of
OL,13,Fschools, families and employers."
OL,15,FExam boards will have to ensure
OL,16,Fwhatever platform is used to deliver
OL,17,Fany proposed on-screen exam meets
OL,18,Fcertain criteria under Ofqual's
OL,19,Fproposals.
