OL,3,CSeveral GCSE and A-level exams could
OL,4,Cbe taken on screen from 2030
OL,6,FThe consultation for on-screen exams
OL,7,Fwill run until March 5. Once it has
OL,8,Fconcluded and the responses are
OL,9,Fanalysed, a technical consultation
OL,10,Fwould be run to put in place the
OL,11,Fassessment rules before exam boards
OL,12,Fcan submit their potential
OL,13,Fqualifications.
OL,15,FIf these are approved, the new
OL,16,Fspecifications would ideally be in
OL,17,Fschools three years before the first
OL,18,Fexams happen, Ofqual said, meaning the
OL,19,Fend of the decade is a "minimum"
OL,20,Ftimeline for the first exams using
OL,21,Fscreens.
