OL,3,CSeveral GCSE and A-level exams could
OL,4,Cbe taken on screen from 2030
OL,6,FThree of the major exam boards had
OL,7,Flaid out proposals to introduce on-
OL,8,Fscreen assessments.
OL,10,FIn 2023, AQA set out plans for GCSE
OL,11,FItalian and Polish reading and
OL,12,Flistening components to move on screen
OL,13,Fby 2026, with hopes for at least one
OL,14,Fmajor subject to follow by 2030.
OL,16,FOCR had proposed a digitally assessed
OL,17,FGCSE in computer science for pupils
OL,18,Fstarting their course in 2025, and
OL,19,FPearson Edexcel planned to offer a
OL,20,Fchoice to sit on-screen GCSE English
OL,21,Fexams from summer 2025.
